{
  "texts": [
    "Tomato is one of the most important and widely cultivated vegetables worldwide.",
    "It is also susceptible to various diseases caused by pathogens, fungi, and bacteria, which can significantly reduce tomato yield and quality.",
    "Early detection of plant diseases is critical to prevent the spread of the disease and minimize crop losses [2].",
    "Traditional methods of disease detection, such as visual inspection, are time-consuming and may not always be accurate.",
    "Therefore, there is a growing interest in using artificial intelligence (AI) to detect and diagnose plant diseases."
  ]
}